						               													<description>Kaiju City is constantly plagued by giant rampaging monsters. For this reason, the city is always rebuilding itself in the hopes of fending off the latest giant monster attack. Will this be the end of Kaiju City or will the monsters be defeated? Pick a side and play against your friends to decide the fate of Kaiju City!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Kaiju City 2-6 players divide into two teams. One team controls four titanic skyscraper-toppling monsters, the other directs the efforts of Kaiju City to defend itself and drive off its invaders.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The monster team stomps their way through the city destroying as much as they can as quickly as possible using special powers like poison breath and causing earthquakes. Destroy the city and the monsters win! This team provides a lighter gaming experience allowing monster players to focus on stomping their way to victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The City team draws and places tiles allowing them to manage resources and mobilize the military to engage and destroy the invaders. Kill four monsters and the City team wins! This team provides a more strategic gaming experience as the city players must choose their tile placement carefully as well as managing their resources to ensure that they have what they need to drive the monsters from their beloved Kaiju City.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Experience an asymmetrical game design and have several tons of fun crashing through buildings and zapping monsters with your lightning cannon!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
